{
 "name": "RPlog_New_Republic_Counter-Attack",
 "title": "New Republic Counter-Attack",
 "summary": "Rear Admiral Mora Rodriga leads the recreated New Republic fleet, flagship Reprisal, into a system to challenge the Imperial armada and protect the evacuation transport carrying the Senator of Cochran. Ghost Squadron, led by Krieg and including pilots like Ridge Archilles and Gyzen, launches alongside Shadow Eagles and Falcon Squadron to engage the Imperial bombers and capital ships. Aboard the Malevolence, the bedridden Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin directs the Imperial defense, ordering turbolaser fire that ultimately destroys the sacrificial cruiser GSS Gabriel as it shields fleeing civilians. The chaotic starfighter melee rages on, with Imperial pilots like Tellain and Republic Ghosts trading fire across the void.",
